  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tbsp of avocado oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Caramelize the onion by cooking it for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly to prevent burning.",
    "Add the chili powder and cumin. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the narutomaki pieces. Cook for 2 minutes, flipping halfway through.",
    "Warm the corn tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing 1-2 pieces of narutomaki onto each tortilla, followed by a spoonful of salsa, a sprinkle of caramelized onion, and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
